---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Free PDF to Quiz">
  <div class="max-w-[820px] mx-auto px-md sm:px-lg py-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-display-lg text-ink mb-lg">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="text-body-md text-body space-y-md leading-relaxed">
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> June 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-display-sm text-ink mt-xl">1. No Data Collection</h2>
      <p>
        Free PDF to Quiz does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data. The entire application runs client-side in your browser. Your PDF files, generated quizzes, and any other data you interact with never leave your device.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-display-sm text-ink mt-xl">2. No File Uploads</h2>
      <p>
        When you use our PDF to quiz generator, your PDF is processed entirely in your browser using PDF.js. No file data is uploaded to any server. There are no backend servers, databases, or cloud storage involved in the quiz generation process.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-display-sm text-ink mt-xl">3. Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We use Google Analytics to collect anonymous, aggregate page-view data (pages visited, browser type, and country). This helps us understand how the site is used and improve it. Google Analytics may set cookies on your device. No PDF content, quiz data, or personally identifying information is ever sent to Google or any other third party. You can opt out by using a browser extension such as the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" class="text-link hover:text-link-deep transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics Opt-out Add-on</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-display-sm text-ink mt-xl">4. Local Storage</h2>
      <p>
        The only data stored on your device is your theme preference (light/dark mode) in localStorage. This is strictly optional and under your control. You can clear it at any time through your browser settings.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-display-sm text-ink mt-xl">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>
        This website loads the Inter font from rsms.me and uses a CDN-hosted Astro runtime. No personal data is shared with these services. The font request is subject to standard HTTP request headers (IP address, user agent) which are not logged or tracked by us.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-display-sm text-ink mt-xl">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        If this policy changes in the future, the updated version will be posted on this page with a revised date. Since we do not collect user data, there is no need for notification or consent workflows.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-display-sm text-ink mt-xl">7. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this privacy policy, please reach out at <a href="mailto:zunnoorainqureshi@gmail.com" class="text-link hover:text-link-deep transition-colors">zunnoorainqureshi@gmail.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
